    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Crimson Order:</strong> 6th, 11th, and 17th level</em></p>\n<p>You've learned to enhance your kata. As a bonus action while wielding a monk weapon, you can expend 1 focus point to cause the area within 5 feet of you to become difficult terrain for hostile creatures for 1 minute. This area travels with you, and affected creatures within the area can not make opportunity attacks.</p>\n<p>At 11th level, the range of this area increases to 15 feet, and at 17th level, the range of this area increases to 30 feet.</p>",
